review.reviewBody: i love their food. Always fresh and tasty also, they are worth the price. I love ordering food from this restaurant and i totally recommend this store. I ordered multiple times and different items . They were so good.
Everything was cold and drenched with oil, save your time, dont order from this place.
Taste was good but quantity was very less
Amritsari Kulcha is too good but Samosa Each is old like it's to oily
Sarson Ka Saag was super tasty 😋, but was very spicy for me. Do mention if you like less spicy food. It tastes like India. Makki Roti  was also well cooked. I enjoyed my meal.
